want to play around,

228
00:10:41,111 --> 00:10:42,871
but are you finished with
your summer homework?

229
00:10:44,611 --> 00:10:45,881
What are you talking about?

230
00:10:45,881 --> 00:10:49,751
You can finish homework like that
in just three days.

231
00:10:49,751 --> 00:10:52,281
Take care of all of that
bothersome stuff

232
00:10:52,281 --> 00:10:56,221
so you can have fun without
having to worry about it.

233
00:10:56,221 --> 00:10:59,091
That's how you enjoy
your summer vacation!

234
00:11:00,661 --> 00:11:03,061
Why is she so smart?

235
00:11:04,701 --> 00:11:08,291
The next day was yet again
a beautiful day.

236
00:11:08,731 --> 00:11:10,371
It was on this day

237
00:11:10,371 --> 00:11:13,111
that we had the SOS Brigade
Cicada Capturing Competition.

238
00:11:13,111 --> 00:11:15,841
It looks like each of us did try,
in their own way,

239
00:11:15,841 --> 00:11:18,001
but of course, or something
to that effect,

240
00:11:18,411 --> 00:11:20,401
the winner ended up
being Haruhi.

241
00:11:22,481 --> 00:11:24,451
The next day,
we met up,

242
00:11:24,451 --> 00:11:26,751
even though we had no idea
what was going on.

243
00:11:26,751 --> 00:11:28,351
And we continued to have no idea
what was going on,

244
00:11:28,351 --> 00:11:30,391
even as we were made to
wear frog costumes,

245
00:11:30,391 --> 00:11:34,521
and pass out balloons in front of a
supermarket as our part-time job.

246
00:11:37,401 --> 00:11:38,531
Are you all right?

247
