for Mikuru's sake.

254
00:11:57,651 --> 00:11:59,881
We worked for that?

255
00:12:00,391 --> 00:12:05,421
Mikuru, you can wear it whenever
you want. You have my permission!

256
00:12:05,421 --> 00:12:06,621
Ribbit.

257
00:12:14,071 --> 00:12:19,971
That night, a single phone call
stole me away from my slumber.

258
00:12:21,841 --> 00:12:22,741
Dammit.

259
00:12:26,411 --> 00:12:27,541
Yes?

260
00:12:28,511 --> 00:12:29,671
Whoa!

261
00:12:30,421 --> 00:12:32,251
Kyon...

262
00:12:35,651 --> 00:12:37,221
Is that you,
Miss Asahina?

263
00:12:37,221 --> 00:12:39,421
Yes, it's me...

264
00:12:40,391 --> 00:12:42,691
Something... very not good has...

265
